Text: Can any1 please upload the songs they made when they where The Civilans? i have some of the songs, but i really would like the whole cd.. please, any1=D

sorry mate, but what the hell are you talking about?
The Civilans? Tom Morello, Timmy Commerford and Brad Wilk came from Rage against the machine  and Chris cornell come from soundgarden. But The Civilans?
"Cilivilian" was the name of the band before Audioslave, they released alot of demo material that would later show up on their self titled release "Audioslave".
